description: Convert the measured battery voltage of a standard 12 volt car battery into a percentage state of charge.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask battery state of charge 12 point 5 volts
Alexa, ask battery state of charge to convert 12 point 5 volts
Alexa, ask battery state of charge 12 point 5
name: Battery State of Charge
shortDescription: Convert a measured battery voltage (number) into a state of charge percentage.
